This sketch demonstrates how we can implement modifications
to our shapes using the ControlP5 library.
I use again a simple cubic form and add two modifiers :
- Chamfer Corners
- Chamfer Edges

The process is thus :
-----------------------
  > Declare Mesh
    > Declare Creator
      > Set Creator parameters 
        > Add Creator to Mesh
          >  Declare Modifier
            > Set Modifier parameters
              > Add modifer to Mesh
                > Final Render in draw
                -----------------------


